    <item>
      <title>泰国2026</title>
      <link>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2026/04/13/Thailand2026/</link>
      <guid>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2026/04/13/Thailand2026/</guid>
      <pubDate>4 月 13 日，2026</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="出发前"><a href="#出发前" class="headerlink" title="出发前"></a>出发前</h2><p>从杭州出发，经厦门中转，最终抵达曼谷。这是一段关于美食、风景，以及陪伴“小妞”成长的温暖旅程。</p>
<h2 id="行程"><a href="#行程" class="headerlink" title="行程"></a>行程</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>日期</th>
<th>行程（当地时间）</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>2026&#x2F;02&#x2F;20 星期五</td>
<td><strong>杭州 -&gt; 厦门</strong> 八市、中山路步行街</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2026&#x2F;02&#x2F;21 星期六</td>
<td><strong>厦门 -&gt; 曼谷</strong> EmQuartier、朱拉隆功夜市</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2026&#x2F;02&#x2F;22 星期日</td>
<td><strong>曼谷</strong> The Berkeley Hotel</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2026&#x2F;02&#x2F;23 星期一</td>
<td><strong>曼谷</strong> 暹罗百丽宫、码头夜市</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2026&#x2F;02&#x2F;24 星期二</td>
<td><strong>曼谷</strong> Siam地铁站、Bangkok码头、郑王庙、暹罗天地、朱拉隆功夜市</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2026&#x2F;02&#x2F;25 星期三</td>
<td><strong>曼谷 -&gt; 厦门</strong> 尚泰、机场</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2026&#x2F;02&#x2F;26 星期四</td>
<td><strong>厦门 -&gt; 杭州</strong> SM商场</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="日程"><a href="#日程" class="headerlink" title="日程"></a>日程</h2><h2 id="Day1-厦门·八市的烟火气"><a href="#Day1-厦门·八市的烟火气" class="headerlink" title="Day1 厦门·八市的烟火气"></a>Day1 厦门·八市的烟火气</h2><p>杭州 ✈️ 厦门（中转）✈️ 曼谷</p>
<p>航班在厦门落地，意外收获了厦航提供的免费中转住宿。傍晚时分，拖着行李箱漫步在八市。<br>这里是厦门最地道的烟火气所在，海鲜的鲜香与街头的喧嚣交织。在琳琅满目的摊位间，我们暂别了旅途的疲惫，用味蕾开启了这段旅程。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand02.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand03.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand04.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day2-曼谷·初识暹罗"><a href="#Day2-曼谷·初识暹罗" class="headerlink" title="Day2 曼谷·初识暹罗"></a>Day2 曼谷·初识暹罗</h2><p>厦门 ✈️ 曼谷（中午抵达）</p>
<p>早班机跨越山海，落地曼谷时已是正午。海关通关后，直奔酒店安顿。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand06.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand07.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand08.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>下午的探索从7-11开始——听说这里的网红自制混饮值得一试。果然，泰式甜辣与冰爽口感的碰撞，是旅行中意想不到的惊喜。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand10.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand11.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand12.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day3-曼谷·静谧的休整"><a href="#Day3-曼谷·静谧的休整" class="headerlink" title="Day3 曼谷·静谧的休整"></a>Day3 曼谷·静谧的休整</h2><p>酒店休息</p>
<p>旅途总有小插曲。小妞似乎因昨晚的“7-11特调”闹起了肚子，整个下午都在酒店休息。<br>虽然行程被迫按下暂停键，但不得不承认，泰国的酒店品质确实令人惊喜。在舒适的房间里陪孩子静养，也是一种独特的旅行体验。<br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand05.jpg"></p>
<h2 id="Day4-曼谷·湄南河的夜色"><a href="#Day4-曼谷·湄南河的夜色" class="headerlink" title="Day4 曼谷·湄南河的夜色"></a>Day4 曼谷·湄南河的夜色</h2><p>南昭河夜游 + 自助餐</p>
<p>小妞的状态好转，我们决定在夜晚重新出发。<br>湄南河夜游是曼谷的必体验项目。华灯初上，两岸灯火倒映在波光粼粼的河面上，吹着晚风，享用一顿丰盛的自助餐，疲惫感一扫而空。<br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand14.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand13.jpg"></p>
<h2 id="Day5-曼谷·郑王庙"><a href="#Day5-曼谷·郑王庙" class="headerlink" title="Day5 曼谷·郑王庙"></a>Day5 曼谷·郑王庙</h2><p>郑王庙拍照 · 暹罗天地 · 朱拉隆功夜市</p>
<p>小妞完全恢复了活力！<br>上午，我们在郑王庙（Wat Arun）留下了最美的合影，夕阳下的白塔金碧辉煌，仿佛穿越了时空。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand15.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand16.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand17.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>傍晚转战暹罗天地，在商场里偶遇了泡泡玛特（Pop Mart）的限定陈列，小家伙看得目不转睛。<br>夜幕降临，朱拉隆功夜市的烟火气再次点燃。这里汇聚了最地道的泰式小吃，每一口都是惊喜。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid r73"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand18.jpg" alt="暹罗天地的泡泡玛特"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand19.jpg" alt="暹罗天地的泡泡玛特"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day6-曼谷·归途前的最后时光"><a href="#Day6-曼谷·归途前的最后时光" class="headerlink" title="Day6 曼谷·归途前的最后时光"></a>Day6 曼谷·归途前的最后时光</h2><p>最后一天，在商场里为亲友挑选了些许特产。<br>有趣的是，在曼谷的商场里竟然也能找到太二酸菜鱼，而且支持微信扫码点餐。这份熟悉的“中国味”，在异国他乡显得格外亲切。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand20.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand21.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2026-0406/Thailand22.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day7-厦门·回归与休整"><a href="#Day7-厦门·回归与休整" class="headerlink" title="Day7 厦门·回归与休整"></a>Day7 厦门·回归与休整</h2><p>曼谷 ✈️ 厦门 ✈️ 杭州</p>
<p>清晨 7 点，航班降落在厦门。<br>为了赶下午的返程航班，我们在机场附近酒店小憩了一上午。午后，在SM 城市广场简单逛吃，感受这座城市的悠闲节奏。<br>傍晚，带着满满的回忆与特产，飞回杭州。</p>
<h2 id="旅行小记"><a href="#旅行小记" class="headerlink" title="旅行小记"></a>旅行小记</h2><p>• 关于行程：厦门中转虽意外，但八市的夜宵值得等待；曼谷行程紧凑，但孩子的健康永远是第一位的。<br>• 关于美食：7-11 特调、湄南河自助餐、朱拉隆功夜市、太二酸菜鱼……味蕾的满足感贯穿全程。<br>• 关于体验：泰国的酒店品质普遍在线，郑王庙的日落是摄影爱好者的天堂。</p>
<h2 id="感受"><a href="#感受" class="headerlink" title="感受"></a>感受</h2><p>旅行不仅是看风景，更是陪孩子慢慢长大。</p>
]]></description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本东京2025</title>
      <link>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2025/07/30/Japan2025/</link>
      <guid>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2025/07/30/Japan2025/</guid>
      <pubDate>7 月 30 日，2025</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>暑假，我们一家从杭州出发，经上海浦东搭乘全日空直飞成田。这是一段关于美食、风景，以及陪伴“小妞”成长的温暖旅程。从东京的繁华到富士山的壮丽，再到镰仓的海风，每一站都留下了难忘的回忆。</p>
<h2 id="行程"><a href="#行程" class="headerlink" title="行程"></a>行程</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">日期</th>
<th align="left">行程（当地时间）</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;18 (周五)</strong></td>
<td align="left">杭州 → 上海 → 东京</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;19 (周六)</strong></td>
<td align="left">东京</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;20 (周日)</strong></td>
<td align="left">东京</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;21 (周一)</strong></td>
<td align="left">东京 → 河口湖</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;22 (周二)</strong></td>
<td align="left">东京</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;23 (周三)</strong></td>
<td align="left">东京 → 镰仓 → 热海</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;24 (周四)</strong></td>
<td align="left">热海 → 三岛 → 热海</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;25 (周五)</strong></td>
<td align="left">热海 → 小田原 → 热海 → 东京</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;26 (周六)</strong></td>
<td align="left">东京</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><strong>2025&#x2F;07&#x2F;27 (周日)</strong></td>
<td align="left">东京 → 上海 → 杭州</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="日程"><a href="#日程" class="headerlink" title="日程"></a>日程</h2><h2 id="Day1-出发东京"><a href="#Day1-出发东京" class="headerlink" title="Day1 出发东京"></a>Day1 出发东京</h2><p>杭州 🚄 上海 ✈️ 东京（成田）</p>
<p>我们从杭州出发，经上海浦东机场转机，搭乘全日空（ANA）顺利抵达东京成田机场。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid r73"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan01.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan02.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan03.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan04.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan05.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>晚上在民宿周边的超市买了和牛，女儿吃得很开心。<br><span class="image-grid r37"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan07.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan06.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day2-东京·浅草与上野"><a href="#Day2-东京·浅草与上野" class="headerlink" title="Day2 东京·浅草与上野"></a>Day2 东京·浅草与上野</h2><p>继续漫步浅草寺，感受江户风情。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid r73"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan08.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan09.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan10.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan11.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan12.jpg"></span><br></span><br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan13.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan14.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan15.jpg"></span><br></span><br>傍晚转战上野，打卡<strong>烤肉店</strong>，在烟火气中结束第二天。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan16.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan17.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan18.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day3-东京·银座的奢华"><a href="#Day3-东京·银座的奢华" class="headerlink" title="Day3 东京·银座的奢华"></a>Day3 东京·银座的奢华</h2><p>程充实的一天！<br>上午打卡<strong>银座</strong>，在<strong>GINZA SIX</strong>感受现代建筑的震撼。<br>下午是<strong>文具控</strong>的狂欢——<strong>伊東屋</strong>（Itoya），这座“文具大楼”里应有尽有，小妞挑得不亦乐乎。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan19.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan20.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan21.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>晚上回到上野，在居酒屋<strong>喝啤酒、吃烤串</strong>，享受微醺的夜晚。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan22.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan23.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day4-河口湖"><a href="#Day4-河口湖" class="headerlink" title="Day4 河口湖"></a>Day4 河口湖</h2><p>行程最丰富的一天！<br>早上坐火车前往<strong>河口湖</strong>.<br><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan24.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan25.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>在小镇上意外遇到的美味。<a href="https://koushuya.com/">牛かつ専門店 甲州家</a><br><span class="image-grid r73"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan26.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan27.jpg" alt="牛かつ専門店 甲州家"></span><br></span></p>
<p><strong>富士急乐园</strong>。里面的<strong>过山车</strong>太刺激了，小妞虽然害怕，但全程都在尖叫中体验了一把“速度与激情”。</p>
<p><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan28.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan29.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan30.jpg"></span><br></span><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan31.jpg"></p>
<p>下午在<strong>富士山下的罗森网红店</strong><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/%E7%BD%97%E6%A3%AE%EF%BC%88%E6%B2%B3%E5%8F%A3%E6%B9%96%E7%AB%99%E5%89%8D%E5%BA%97%EF%BC%89/@35.4986175,138.7645923,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m12!1m5!3m4!2zMzXCsDI5JzU1LjciTiAxMzjCsDQ2JzAxLjkiRQ!8m2!3d35.4988056!4d138.7671944!3m5!1s0x60195e28296a89bf:0x611c18cefec8cb56!8m2!3d35.4986175!4d138.7671672!16s%2Fg%2F11b7k_0b59?authuser=2&entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDQwOC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw==">ローソン 河口湖駅前店</a>拍照打卡，可惜当天天气不佳，云层太厚，富士山若隐若现……<br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan.jpg"></p>
<p>晚上，全家<strong>第一次尝试了一兰拉面</strong>，汤底浓郁，味道惊艳！<br>女儿在地铁站还发现了网红冰淇淋。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan32.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan33.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan34.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day5-东京·美食"><a href="#Day5-东京·美食" class="headerlink" title="Day5 东京·美食"></a>Day5 东京·美食</h2><p>中午去吃了<strong>寿司朗</strong>（Sushi Ron），听说在中国排队要排很久，没想到在东京也要排，不过大概只等了 15 分钟，性价比超高！<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan35.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan36.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan37.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>下午逛了<strong>秋叶原</strong>，在百货店里淘了不少宝贝。<br><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan38.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan39.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>晚上，小妞心心念念的<strong>活钓鱿鱼</strong>终于安排上了，新鲜到还在动！<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan40.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan41.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan42.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan45.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan43.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan44.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan46.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day6-镰仓·热海"><a href="#Day6-镰仓·热海" class="headerlink" title="Day6 镰仓·热海"></a>Day6 镰仓·热海</h2><p>离开东京，前往<strong>镰仓</strong>。<br><span class="image-grid r46"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan47.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan48.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>到了镰仓，吃个午餐先<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan49.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan50.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan51.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>打卡了『<a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E7%81%8C%E7%AF%AE%E9%AB%98%E6%89%8B">灌篮高手</a>』经典的<strong>海边铁道口</strong>和 <a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E9%8E%8C%E5%80%89%E9%AB%98%E6%A0%A1%E5%89%8D%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99">鎌倉高校前駅</a>，电车驶过的瞬间，仿佛电影场景重现。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan52.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan53.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan54.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan55.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>傍晚抵达<a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E7%86%B1%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82"><strong>热海</strong></a>，入住海边的酒店，为第二天的日出做准备。</p>
<h2 id="Day7-热海·日出"><a href="#Day7-热海·日出" class="headerlink" title="Day7 热海·日出"></a>Day7 热海·日出</h2><p>凌晨 4 点，全家起床看<strong>海上日出</strong>，海面上的金光闪闪，美得让人屏息。<br><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan56.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan57.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>酒店房间正对大海<br><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan58.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan59.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan60.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>中午去找了 N 年前吃过的<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/%E6%B7%A1%E5%B3%B6%E5%AF%BF%E5%8F%B8/@35.0964846,139.0727729,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x6019be6722087623:0xb53a1751a34922a8!8m2!3d35.0964846!4d139.0753478!16s%2Fg%2F1tgz5k05?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDQwOC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw=="><strong>淡岛寿司</strong></a>，重新回味一下当年的味道，依然鲜美。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan61.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan62.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan63.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan64.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan65.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan66.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>傍晚坐火车去了热海旁边的<strong>三岛市</strong>，体验了一家路边美食烧烤，烟火气十足。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan67.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan68.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan69.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan70.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<h2 id="Day8-小田原·热海"><a href="#Day8-小田原·热海" class="headerlink" title="Day8 小田原·热海"></a>Day8 小田原·热海</h2><p>小妞换上<strong>日本民族服饰</strong>（和服），去<strong>小田原城</strong>拍了一系列美美的照片，古风满满！</p>
<p><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan71.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan72.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan73.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan74.jpg"></span><br></span></p>
<p>晚上回到热海，体验了日本的<strong>花火大会</strong>，夜空中绽放的烟花，照亮了整个海面。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan75.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan76.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan77.jpg"></span><br></span><br>午夜时分，搭火车回到东京，住在<strong>王子酒店</strong>，结束这一天。</p>
<h2 id="Day9-东京"><a href="#Day9-东京" class="headerlink" title="Day9 东京"></a>Day9 东京</h2><p>行程的最后一天，随便逛逛。<br>去了<strong>涉谷</strong>，路过那个<strong>人流量最大的十字路口</strong>，感受东京的快节奏。<br><span class="image-grid portrait"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan78.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan79.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan80.jpg"></span><br></span><br>品尝了<strong>极味肉肉大米</strong>，味道独特，分量十足。<br><span class="image-grid landscape"><span class="grid-item"><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan81.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan82.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan83.jpg"><br><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2025-0709/Japan84.jpg"></span><br></span><br>晚上住到<strong>机场酒店</strong>，为第二天的返程做准备。</p>
<h2 id="Day10-返程"><a href="#Day10-返程" class="headerlink" title="Day10 返程"></a>Day10 返程</h2><p>搭早上 9 点的飞机，带着满满的回忆飞回杭州。<br>这次日本之旅，有美食、有风景、有刺激，更有小妞的成长。</p>
<h2 id="感受"><a href="#感受" class="headerlink" title="感受"></a>感受</h2><ul>
<li><strong>关于体验</strong>：富士急乐园的过山车太刺激了，小田原城的和服拍照超美，热海的花火大会浪漫满分。</li>
<li><strong>关于交通</strong>：东京地铁 + 新干线 + 地方火车，换乘虽多但很准时，行李直挂很方便。</li>
<li><strong>关于美食</strong>：寿司朗、一兰拉面、活钓鱿鱼、极味肉肉大米……味蕾的满足感贯穿全程。</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚2023</title>
      <link>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2023/12/27/Malaysia2023/</link>
      <guid>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2023/12/27/Malaysia2023/</guid>
      <pubDate>12 月 27 日，2023</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>5月去了一趟香港澳门，也不算是出国，暑假尾巴终于走出国门，转机新加坡去了马来西亚，榴莲我们来了。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_01.jpg" alt="杭州机场的酷航"></p>
<p>杭州机场的酷航波音梦幻787大客机。几年前去新加坡的时候已经坐过一次，这次去大马，买的新加坡航空实际执飞是酷航。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_02.jpg" alt="茨厂街"></p>
<p>到了KUL，就是各种逛吃。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_03.jpg" alt="黄亚华的鸡翅"></p>
<p>黄亚华的鸡翅是一定要来吃的</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_04.jpg" alt="吉隆坡街头"></p>
<p>吉隆坡街头。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_05.jpg" alt="SS2"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_06.jpg" alt="SS2"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_07.jpg" alt="榕城的榴莲"></p>
<p>SS2，吉隆坡专门的榴莲市场，吃起来。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_08.jpg" alt="槟城"></p>
<p>转机到槟城，订的是滚石酒店，房间阳台打开就是泳池。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_09.jpg" alt="沙滩"></p>
<p>酒店后门的沙滩，逛逛，看看夕阳，骑骑马……</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_10.jpg" alt="小娘惹"></p>
<p>老婆喜欢的小娘惹，女儿换上一套娘惹服，拍点照片</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_11.jpg" alt="槟城街头"></p>
<p>来到古城，左边是N年前第一次来槟城，那时女儿还是小宝宝，右边是今年的女儿。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_12.jpg" alt="壁画留影"></p>
<p>壁画留影</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_13.jpg" alt="张弼士故居"></p>
<p>张弼士故居，进来逛逛，听说还能吃饭住宿，以后可以来体验一下。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023my_14.jpg" alt="张弼士故居"></p>
<p>这也是N年前第一次来槟城，好不容易找到了这家小店，不知道下次打卡女儿是不是已经和妈妈一样高呢？</p>
]]></description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳门香港2023</title>
      <link>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2023/12/26/HongKong2023/</link>
      <guid>https://paulreina.com/p/p/2023/12/26/HongKong2023/</guid>
      <pubDate>12 月 26 日，2023</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>疫情于今年年初终于结束，自从2020年过年的菲律宾之行后，一直也没出国旅游，今年出去的第一站选择了澳门+香港。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_01.png" alt="澳门机场"></p>
<p>第一次来到澳门机场，感觉挺小的。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_02.png" alt="大三巴附近"></p>
<p>去酒店简单安置一下，到大三巴附近转转</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_03.png" alt="大三巴牌坊"></p>
<p>大三巴牌坊是澳门天主之母教堂正面前壁的遗址，属于“圣保禄学院天主之母教堂遗址”的组成部分之一，亦是澳门的标志性建筑物之一。“大三巴”一名为华人对圣保禄学院及教堂的称呼，出自圣保禄的葡萄牙文“São Paulo”的汉语译音。 </p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_04.png" alt="官也街"></p>
<p>晚上来到官也街逛逛吃点好吃的，比如牛杂，可惜大家都觉得还不如大三巴边上的牛杂小摊味道好。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_05.png" alt="渔人码头"></p>
<p>第二天，来到渔人码头逛逛。<br>澳门渔人码头是澳门首个主题公园和仿欧美渔人码头的购物中心。澳门渔人码头建于外港新填海区孙逸仙大马路对开，邻近新港澳码头。由何鸿燊及周锦辉投资兴建，总投资约为澳门币18.5亿，经过5年时间筹备与兴建。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_10.png" alt="东望洋灯塔"></p>
<p>登山想去逛个灯塔，结果上山的中途走错了路……</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_06.png" alt="永利皇宫"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_08.png" alt="永利皇宫"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_07.png" alt="永利皇宫"></p>
<p>傍晚，来到永利皇宫，排队坐🚠，逛逛洋气的“娱乐”皇宫，女儿对这儿的一家甜品赞不绝口，过年去的话准备再次光顾一下。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_09.png" alt="澳门的酒店"></p>
<p>永利皇宫周边的娱乐业酒店。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_11.png" alt="港珠澳大桥"></p>
<p>坐大巴经港珠澳大桥前往香港，女儿已经计划去玩海洋公园和水上乐园。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_16.png" alt="海洋公园"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_13.png" alt="水上乐园"></p>
<p>分两天前往海洋公园和水上乐园</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_15.png" alt="海洋公园"></p>
<p>在海洋公园偶遇明星一家。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_17.png" alt="海洋公园"></p>
<p>重温了小妞第一次来HongKong时的场景</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_12.png" alt="香港街头"></p>
<p>香港街头，离我们住的酒店不远的一家煲仔饭，傍晚时分排起长队</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_14.png" alt="叮叮车"></p>
<p>来过香港很多次，一直没坐过叮叮车，小妞长大了，现在可以拿着GoPro坐着叮叮车自拍了</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="https://imgs.paulreina.com/2023-1012/2023hk_18.png" alt="天星小轮"></p>
<p>结束了这一轮的澳门香港游。<br>香港，确实已经不是10年前的香港，旧地重游，感觉酒店太贵房间太小，城市几乎没有大的变化，老婆说这几年应该不会再来香港了。</p>
<p>PS：2024年春节已经计划再去澳门，怀念澳门的美食，期待再次出发。</p>
]]></description>
    </item>
